        "System Updated"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对的。Retail_CouponSystem在第三阶段被系统创建，Retail_Inventory在第四阶段被系统更新。而且每个阶段都要保留之前的状态，形成层级关系。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Retail_CouponSystem",
        "Retail_Inventory",
        "System Created",
        "System Updated",
        "Created",
        "Updated"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我先搭建基础框架。第一阶段是Created v1，第二阶段是Updated v2，同时保留Created v1作为子状态。第三阶段是System Created (Retail_CouponSystem) v3，叠加前面的所有状态。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Created v1",
        "Updated v2",
        "System Created (Retail_CouponSystem) v3"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "等等，第四阶段的System Updated后面，是不是还应该有个System Created的子状态？我记得Retail_Inventory在被更新之前，应该先被创建。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "System Updated",
