    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "repair",
      "utterance": "您说得对，我漏掉了。第四阶段System Updated (Retail_Inventory) v4下面，确实需要加上System Created (Retail_Inventory)作为子状态，表示这个库存模块是先创建后更新的完整链路。",
